<!-- gsd-project-start source:PROJECT.md -->
## Project

**FinanceiroVK вЂ” Flat-File Edition**

AplicaГ§ГЈo web de controle financeiro pessoal com arquitetura flat-file. Frontend estГЎtico (HTML/JS) hospedado no GitHub Pages, dados armazenados em arquivos JSON no repositГіrio, e escrita de dados via GitHub Actions disparadas por Issues criadas pelo frontend via API do GitHub. IntegraГ§ГЈo com Gemini AI para OCR de comprovantes.

**Core Value:** O usuГЎrio consegue registrar e visualizar suas transaГ§Гµes financeiras de forma rГЎpida e confiГЎvel, com dados versionados e sob seu controle total no GitHub.

### Constraints

- **Hosting:** GitHub Pages (site estГЎtico, sem server-side rendering)
- **Dados:** Flat-file JSON no repo (sem banco de dados externo)
- **Escrita:** Via GitHub Actions apenas (sem endpoint HTTP prГіprio)
- **Custo:** Zero вЂ” todos os serviГ§os usados sГЈo gratuitos (GitHub Pages, Actions, API Gemini free tier)
- **LatГЄncia de escrita:** Salvamentos nГЈo sГЈo instantГўneos вЂ” dependem do ciclo Issue в†’ Action в†’ commit (segundos a minutos)
- **SeguranГ§a:** Sem autenticaГ§ГЈo; repo pode ser privado com GitHub Pages habilitado
- **IA:** Gemini API com key gerenciada via GitHub Secrets, injetada no build
<!-- gsd-project-end -->

<!-- gsd-stack-start source:codebase/STACK.md -->
## Technology Stack

## Languages
- JavaScript (ES6+) вЂ” All server-side logic (`.gs` files) and client-side UI (inline `<script>` in `.html` files)
- HTML5 вЂ” UI templates for Web App and Sidebars (`WebApp.html`, `Sidebar.html`, `ComprovanteSidebar.html`, `Relatorio.html`, `ConfiguracoesUI.html`)
- CSS3 вЂ” Inline styles with CSS Custom Properties (all `.html` files use `:root` variables for theming)
## Runtime
- Google Apps Script V8 runtime (configured in `appsscript.json` в†’ `"runtimeVersion": "V8"`)
- Timezone: `America/Sao_Paulo`
- Exception logging: Stackdriver
- Server-side: Google Apps Script engine (`.gs` files)
- Client-side: Browser sandbox within Google Apps Script `HtmlService` iframe
- None вЂ” Google Apps Script has no package manager. All dependencies are either built-in GAS services or loaded via CDN in HTML files.
## Frameworks
- Google Apps Script (GAS) вЂ” Server-side framework. Provides `SpreadsheetApp`, `UrlFetchApp`, `HtmlService`, `Utilities`, `Logger`
- No framework вЂ” Vanilla HTML/CSS/JS with `google.script.run` bridge for server calls
- Chart.js 4.4.7 вЂ” Loaded via CDN in `WebApp.html` line 154: `https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/chart.js@4.4.7/dist/chart.umd.min.js`
- Used for doughnut, bar, and comparison charts on the Dashboard tab
- Not detected вЂ” No test framework or test files present
- No build tooling вЂ” Files are directly deployed to Google Apps Script editor or via `clasp`
- No transpilation, bundling, or minification pipeline
## Key Dependencies
- Google Sheets API (via `SpreadsheetApp`) вЂ” Primary data store for all financial data. Used in every `.gs` file
- Google Gemini API (v1beta, model `gemini-2.5-flash`) вЂ” AI features: receipt analysis, category suggestion, monthly insights. Client in `Gemini.gs`
- Chart.js 4.4.7 (CDN) вЂ” Interactive dashboard charts in `WebApp.html`
- `SpreadsheetApp` вЂ” CRUD on spreadsheet tabs (TransaГ§Гµes, Config, OrГ§amento, PoupanГ§a, etc.)
- `UrlFetchApp` вЂ” HTTP calls to Gemini API (`Gemini.gs` line 292)
- `HtmlService` вЂ” Serves HTML UI as sidebar or standalone Web App (`Code.gs` lines 39-43, 80-104)
- `Utilities` вЂ” Date formatting with timezone (`Utils.gs`, `Transacoes.gs`)
- `Logger` вЂ” Server-side logging for debugging (`Utils.gs` line 34, `Gemini.gs` line 314)
- `google.script.run` вЂ” Client-to-server bridge used in all `.html` files to call GAS functions
- `FileReader` API вЂ” Image/PDF upload in `ComprovanteSidebar.html` and `WebApp.html`
- Base64 encoding вЂ” Image data sent to Gemini via `inline_data` in `Gemini.gs` line 72
## Configuration
- All configuration stored in the `вљ™пёЏ Config` spreadsheet tab as key-value pairs (column A = key, column B = value)
- `.env` file: Not applicable вЂ” GAS doesn't use environment files
- Configuration keys defined in `Setup.gs` lines 47-80, read via `Configuracoes.gs`
- `gemini_api_key` вЂ” Google Gemini API key (stored in spreadsheet Config tab)
- `usar_ia` вЂ” Boolean toggle for AI features
- `nome_pessoa1` / `nome_pessoa2` вЂ” Person names
- `salario_pessoa1` / `salario_pessoa2` вЂ” Monthly salary reference
- `moeda` вЂ” Currency symbol (default: `R$`)
- `dia_fechamento_fatura` / `dia_pagamento_fatura` вЂ” Credit card billing cycle (per-person overrides available)
- `meta_economia_pessoa1` / `meta_economia_pessoa2` вЂ” Monthly savings goal
- `meta_poupanca_pessoa1` / `meta_poupanca_pessoa2` вЂ” Savings account goal
- `metodos_pagamento` вЂ” Pipe-separated custom payment methods
- `mostrar_centavos` вЂ” Display cents toggle
- `https://www.googleapis.com/auth/spreadsheets` вЂ” Full spreadsheet access
- `https://www.googleapis.com/auth/script.container.ui` вЂ” Sidebar and menu UI
- `https://www.googleapis.com/auth/script.external_request` вЂ” External HTTP requests (Gemini API)
- `executeAs`: `USER_DEPLOYING` вЂ” Runs under the deployer's identity
- `access`: `ANYONE` вЂ” Public access to the Web App
## Design System / Theming
- `--p: #1a237e` вЂ” Primary (Indigo 900)
- `--s: #3949ab` вЂ” Secondary (Indigo 600)
- `--ok: #2e7d32` вЂ” Success/Revenue (Green 800)
- `--err: #c62828` вЂ” Error/Expense (Red 800)
- `--warn: #e65100` вЂ” Warning (Orange 900)
- `--bg: #f0f2ff` вЂ” Background
- `--card: #fff` вЂ” Card surface
- `--txt: #37474f` вЂ” Text (Blue Grey 800)
- `--border: #c5cae9` вЂ” Border (Indigo 100)
- Font: `'Google Sans', Arial, sans-serif` вЂ” Used in all HTML files
## Platform Requirements
- Google account with access to Google Sheets
- Google Apps Script editor (built into Google Sheets via Extensions в†’ Apps Script)
- Optional: `clasp` CLI for local development (not configured in this project)
- Gemini API key from [aistudio.google.com/apikey](https://aistudio.google.com/apikey) for AI features
- Google Apps Script Web App deployment
- Host: Google infrastructure (no external hosting required)
- Google Sheets as the database (spreadsheet must remain accessible)
- Internet access for Gemini API calls
## File Inventory
- `Code.gs` (155 lines) вЂ” Entry point, constants, Web App `doGet()`, menu, navigation
- `Setup.gs` (294 lines) вЂ” Spreadsheet structure initialization (all tabs)
- `Configuracoes.gs` (246 lines) вЂ” Config CRUD, categories, payment methods, initial data
- `Transacoes.gs` (843 lines) вЂ” Transaction CRUD, budget, reports, savings (largest server file)
- `Gemini.gs` (327 lines) вЂ” Gemini AI integration (receipt, insights, categorization)
- `Dashboard.gs` (309 lines) вЂ” Dashboard tab rendering, profile views, joint analysis
- `Utils.gs` (36 lines) вЂ” Shared utility functions
- `WebApp.html` (2119 lines) вЂ” Full standalone Web App (7 tabs, Chart.js integration)
- `Sidebar.html` (~287 lines) вЂ” Legacy sidebar for new transaction
- `ComprovanteSidebar.html` (~310 lines) вЂ” Legacy sidebar for receipt analysis
- `Relatorio.html` (~306 lines) вЂ” Legacy sidebar for monthly report
- `ConfiguracoesUI.html` (~220 lines) вЂ” Legacy sidebar for settings
- `appsscript.json` (15 lines) вЂ” GAS manifest with OAuth scopes and Web App config
- `README.md` (231 lines) вЂ” Project documentation
